@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lgbgbc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v2 * v1) + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.91) * (v2 + 0.25 * v2 + 0.72)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = (v1 - ((v2 + 0.02 + v0 + 0.71) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.30)))
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.13 / tmp + 0.02) - (v1 + 0.75 - v2 + 0.01)) - (0.18 + (v1 + 0.88 / v0 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
